                                              Privacy & Security Statement


     Welcome to the NASA Goddard Space Flight Center's FOIA homepage. We
    hope you find this site informative and that it will facilitate your
          efforts to obtain information about NASA/GSFC activities.
                       Location: Building 8, Room 441
    Hours of Operation: Mon.-Fri. (excluding federal holidays) 8:00a.m. -
                                  4:00p.m.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Passed in 1966, the Freedom of Information Act provides the public and
   industry a means of acquiring information about government activities.
